race.comment: TARPS (2) has threatened here his last three and comes back in grade off the latest. Draws awkwardly again but has a 3kg claim today and this is winnable with average luck. HOLLYWOOD EPIC (1) won here this grade from the pace and then gave it away late on the turf beaten 2L in much stronger than this. Maps for the run of the race and the 3kg claim brings him right into it. MINTO'S PRINCE (4) led and was an easy Maiden winner here on debut. Led in that but the gate is awkward today. Fitter and he has plenty of scope for improvement. CAT CALL (6) may need one more run but would be competitive finding his best. He also needs a good ride.
